    "text": "with his new sidekick, Fred."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.8,
    "endTime": 14.8,
    "text": "Why am I here?!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.24,
    "endTime": 16.48,
    "text": "You're in a PG-13 version of Deadpool,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.54,
    "endTime": 19.4,
    "text": "filtered through the prism of child like innocence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.1,
    "endTime": 21.6,
    "text": "-I'm a grown man! -And nobody does child like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.22,
    "endTime": 22.599,
    "text": "innocence like you Fred! Nobody!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.84,
    "endTime": 24.8,
    "text": "I need you, almost as much as you need me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.4,
    "endTime": 26.2,
    "text": "I don't need you, at all!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.22,
    "endTime": 29.799,
    "text": "You need me, to untie you, once we're done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 31.0,
    "text": "(Holiday music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 32.96,
    "text": "Boop!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.12,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "Hi!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.1,
    "endTime": 36.9,
    "text": "I loved your work in Up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.26,
    "endTime": 38.1,
    "text": "I'm sorry?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.32,
    "endTime": 39.9,
    "text": "Don't get too attached."
