    "text": "Yeah, but you're you know, Marvel licensed by FOX."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.72,
    "endTime": 49.98,
    "text": "It's like if The Beatles were produced by Nickleback."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.26,
